        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1. 太阳高度角 "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\alpha _ { s }"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[3]"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                168,
                311,
                341,
                326
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "equation_interline",
            "content": {
                "math_content": "\\sin \\alpha_ {s} = \\cos \\delta \\cos \\varphi \\cos \\omega + \\sin \\delta \\sin \\varphi",
                "math_type": "latex",
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/6cc164f8becf1519975af61d276959d29f09daafbaf772fa845daa0d149421c5.jpg"
                }
            },
            "bbox": [
                349,
                330,
                643,
                344
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "太阳方位角 ???? [4]"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                168,
                348,
                317,
                363
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "equation_interline",
            "content": {
                "math_content": "\\cos \\gamma_ {s} = \\frac {\\sin \\delta - \\sin \\alpha_ {s} \\sin \\varphi}{\\cos \\alpha_ {s} \\cos \\varphi}",
                "math_type": "latex",
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/d3976a2f7a9f6d4f263863ef90996ea37616d215b7d43165f966e8c768661332.jpg"
                }
            },
            "bbox": [
                391,
                367,
                606,
                400
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "其中 ?? 为当地纬度，北纬为正；?? 为太阳时角"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                132,
                403,
                509,
                419
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "equation_interline",
            "content": {
                "math_content": "\\omega = \\frac {\\pi}{1 2} (S T - 1 2),",
                "math_type": "latex",
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/f7212919884f375f6dfbdae58d58a52a8e6900a3c45f7687cc5ab49a76b33a5c.jpg"
                }
            },
            "bbox": [
                425,
                425,
                571,
                454
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "其中 ???? 为当地时间，?? 为太阳赤纬角[5]"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                132,
                458,
                465,
                475
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "equation_interline",
            "content": {
                "math_content": "\\sin \\delta = \\sin \\frac {2 \\pi D}{3 6 5} \\sin \\left(\\frac {2 \\pi}{3 6 0} 2 3. 4 5\\right),",
                "math_type": "latex",
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/30d55eae862efbde721a52df770f7456a7697423d2390737c72e89a721335be1.jpg"
                }
            },
            "bbox": [
                373,
                479,
                621,
                510
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "其中 ?? 为以春分作为第0天起算的天数，例如，若春分是3月21日，则4月1日对应 ?? = 11。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                131,
                514,
                853,
                530
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "2. 法向直接辐射辐照度DNI（单位：kW/m2）是指地球上垂直于太阳光线的平面单位面积上、单位时间内接收到的太阳辐射能量，可按以下公式近似计算[6]"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                132,
                533,
                863,
                568
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "equation_interline",
            "content": {
                "math_content": "\\mathrm{DNI} = G _ {0} \\left[ a + b \\exp \\left(- \\frac {c}{\\sin \\alpha_ {s}}\\right) \\right],",
                "math_type": "latex",
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/7d626a38da014a459e63caa93ed9775c82989471e53f792dcf2c57db1e8611c3.jpg"
                }
            },
            "bbox": [
                366,
                575,
                618,
                605
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "equation_interline",
            "content": {
                "math_content": "a = 0. 4 2 3 7 - 0. 0 0 8 2 1 (6 - H) ^ {2},",
                "math_type": "latex",
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/f9b42f43a5523888c3228ef0ac43d08be95be1ef95145dd0a5dfda775f232b3b.jpg"
                }
            },
            "bbox": [
                369,
                607,
                613,
                621
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "equation_interline",
            "content": {
                "math_content": "b = 0. 5 0 5 5 + 0. 0 0 5 9 5 (6. 5 - H) ^ {2},",
                "math_type": "latex",
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/fc741bf4cb9841ed9264b5a1665637c1c4e18b11233b890f4d014eb74b92e686.jpg"
                }
            },
            "bbox": [
                369,
                623,
                626,
                639
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "equation_interline",
            "content": {
                "math_content": "c = 0. 2 7 1 1 + 0. 0 1 8 5 8 (2. 5 - H) ^ {2},",
                "math_type": "latex",
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/a235eb0fea3dd8a04bf2d97d27319590867e0c70e752993941b456fb58f05e22.jpg"
                }
            },
            "bbox": [
                369,
                640,
                625,
                655
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "其中 "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "G _ { 0 }"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "为太阳常数，其值取为1.366 kW/m2，?? 为海拔高度 (单位：km)。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                132,
                662,
                715,
                678
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "3. 定日镜场的输出热功率 "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "E _ { \\mathrm { f i e l d } }"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "为"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                166,
                682,
                447,
                697
            ]
        },
        {
